    <item>
      <title>拉马福萨吹捧以色列法院在南非投票活动中获胜</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/ramaphosa-touts-israel-court-win-in-south-african-votes-drive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南非总统西里尔·拉马福萨正在利用其政府为结束以色列对哈马斯战争所做的努力，寻求在唯一不受执政的非洲人国民大会控制的省份拉选票。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/ramaphosa-touts-israel-court-win-in-south-african-votes-drive</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普陪审团出示了一张又一张的支票，他签署了偿还科恩的款项</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/trump-jury-shown-check-after-check-he-signed-to-repay-cohen</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周一，纽约陪审团的屏幕上显示了一张又一张的支票，上面有唐纳德·特朗普用黑色记号笔潦草地写下的独特签名。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/trump-jury-shown-check-after-check-he-signed-to-repay-cohen</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 01:26:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>莫迪的家乡在印度激烈的竞选活动中投票</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/modi-s-home-state-votes-in-heated-indian-election-campaign</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度第三阶段选举在总理纳伦德拉·莫迪的家乡古吉拉特邦拉开帷幕，两大主要政党之间的竞选活动变得越来越激烈。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-07/modi-s-home-state-votes-in-heated-indian-election-campaign</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 07 May 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>苏纳克表示下一次英国大选可能比民调显示的更接近</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/sunak-says-next-uk-election-may-be-closer-than-polls-suggest</link>
      <description><![CDATA[里希·苏纳克(Rishi Sunak)表示，下一次英国大选的结果可能比民调显示的结果更接近，这增加了出现悬浮议会的可能性，而没有任何政党拥有全面控制权。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/sunak-says-next-uk-election-may-be-closer-than-polls-suggest</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 18:46:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平呼吁马克龙帮助中国避免“新冷战”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/SD2NA9DWRGG000</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着欧盟日益与美国对安全风险和贸易紧张局势的担忧保持一致，中国国家主席习近平呼吁法国帮助抵御“新冷战”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/SD2NA9DWRGG000</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 17:33:21 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列称哈马斯支持的停火计划未能达成</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/hamas-says-accepts-proposal-for-cease-fire-with-israel</link>
      <description><![CDATA[巴勒斯坦激进组织哈马斯表示已同意加沙地带停火提议，但以色列战时内阁一致拒绝该提议，称其“与以色列的必要要求相去甚远”，使立即暂停战斗的希望破灭。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/hamas-says-accepts-proposal-for-cease-fire-with-israel</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 16:59:07 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举即将进行一半，印度与假新闻作斗争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/india-battles-fake-news-as-election-heads-to-halfway-mark</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着世界上最大规模的选举进入下一阶段，印度正试图打击社交媒体上广泛传播的假新闻。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/india-battles-fake-news-as-election-heads-to-halfway-mark</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 10:25:12 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>澳大利亚谴责中国在其直升机附近发射照明弹</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/australia-complains-over-china-firing-flares-near-its-helicopter</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一架中国战斗机在其军用直升机附近发射照明弹后，澳大利亚政府表示愤怒，这一行为可能会扰乱堪培拉和北京正在改善的关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/australia-complains-over-china-firing-flares-near-its-helicopter</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 09:00:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国节俭的旅行者显示消费者信心疲软</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/china-s-thrifty-travelers-show-consumer-confidence-remains-weak</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在最近为期五天的劳动节假期期间，大量中国游客上路，但仍捂紧钱包，反映出世界第二大经济体的情绪仍然疲软。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-06/china-s-thrifty-travelers-show-consumer-confidence-remains-weak</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 06 May 2024 08:38:09 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
